For this task, the team completed the ApartSmart prototype by refining and enhancing the major user interface screens.
ApartSmart has some major features such as user registration and login, password recovery through OTP, viewing apartment updates and posts,
bill management and payment, receiving notifications, and enabling emergency notifications.

The ApartSmart prototype was built to illustrate how users interact with the application and how apartment management is achieved through the application. 
After refining the ApartSmart prototype, some minor adjustments were made to ensure that the application is user-friendly and easy to understand before 
the actual presentation.
